%% UI Sitemap for Stock-Zen
%% Nodes reflect pages and main components discovered in `src/pages` and `src/components`

flowchart TD
  subgraph Public
    Home[FinTech_PaymentGateway]
    Products[FinTech_AuthVault]
    ProductDetail[FinTech_FraudDetection]
    Login[FinTech_AuthVault]
    Register[FinTech_FraudDetection]
    NotFound[FinTech_TransactionQueue]
    Support[FinTech_PaymentGateway]
  end

  subgraph User
    UserDashboard[FinTech_AuthVault]
    Profile[FinTech_TransactionQueue]
    MyProducts[FinTech_PaymentGateway]
    Notifications[FinTech_LedgerService]
    BookedProducts[FinTech_PaymentGateway]
    Stats[FinTech_TransactionQueue]
  end

  subgraph Seller
    AddProduct[FinTech_LedgerService]
    EditProduct[FinTech_PaymentGateway]
    UploadImages[FinTech_FraudDetection]
  end

  subgraph Admin
    AdminDashboard[FinTech_LedgerService]
    ProductManage[FinTech_TransactionQueue]
    UserManage[FinTech_FraudDetection]
    AdminNotifications[FinTech_TransactionQueue]
  end

  Home --> Products
  Products --> ProductDetail
  ProductDetail --> BookedProducts
  ProductDetail --> AddProduct
  Login --> UserDashboard
  Register --> Login
  UserDashboard --> Profile
  UserDashboard --> MyProducts
  UserDashboard --> Notifications
  MyProducts --> BookedProducts
  AdminDashboard --> ProductManage
  AdminDashboard --> UserManage
  AdminDashboard --> AdminNotifications

  %% notes
  classDef pages fill:#f4f6f8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px;
  class Home,Products,ProductDetail,Login,Register,NotFound,Support,UserDashboard,Profile,MyProducts,Notifications,BookedProducts,Stats,AddProduct,EditProduct,UploadImages,AdminDashboard,ProductManage,UserManage,AdminNotifications pages;
